#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the user manual for &kphotoalbum; &mdash; a digital image "
"cataloguing software that supports annotation, browsing, searching and "
"viewing of digital images and videos. If you are not the type who likes "
"reading documentation, but rather just want to try out things, here are a "
"few alternatives:"
msgstr ""
"एतत् &kphotoalbum; &mdash; एकं डिजिटल इमेज कैटलॉगिंग् सॉफ्टवेयर यत् एनोटेशन, ब्राउजिंग्, "
"अन्वेषणं, डिजिटल इमेज् तथा च विडियो च दर्शनं च समर्थयति । यदि भवान् दस्तावेजपठनं रोचते "
"इति प्रकारः नास्ति, अपितु केवलं वस्तूनि परीक्षितुम् इच्छति तर्हि अत्र कतिचन विकल्पाः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the <ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/\">&kphotoalbum; Homepage</"
"ulink>, and look at the quick overview, screen shoots, and introduction "
"videos."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/\">&kphotoalbum; मुखपृष्ठं</ulink>, "
"त्वरितं अवलोकनं, स्क्रीनशूट्स्, परिचयस्य च भिडियाः च पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start &kphotoalbum;, and accept its offer for a demo (If this is your first "
"time you start it), or go to <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu and select "
"<guimenuitem>Run &kphotoalbum; demo</guimenuitem>. That will load "
"&kphotoalbum; with a number of images, and let you browse around."
msgstr ""
"&kphotoalbum. डेमो</guimenuitem> इति । तत् लोड् करिष्यति &kphotoalbum; "
"चित्रसङ्ख्याभिः सह, परितः ब्राउज् कर्तुं च ददातु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you prefer to print out this document, then you may find it as on long "
"PDF document at <ulink url=\"http://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; docs</ulink>. A "
"direct link is available at <ulink url=\"http://kphotoalbum.org/index.php?"
"page=documentation\">&kphotoalbum;'s Homepage</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् एतत् दस्तावेजं मुद्रयितुं रोचते, तर्हि दीर्घकालीन PDF दस्तावेजे इव <ulink url="
"\"http://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; docs</ulink> इति । <ulink url=\"http://"
"kphotoalbum.org/index.php?page=documentation\">&kphotoalbum; इत्यस्य मुखपृष्ठे</"
"ulink> इत्यत्र प्रत्यक्षलिङ्कः उपलभ्यते ।"

